==== 沙門氏菌（''Salmonella enterica''） ====
[[沙門氏菌|沙門氏菌]]會表現一種 LuxR 的同源蛋白 SdiA，但並不會轉譯出AHL合成酶。SdiA可偵測由其他細菌種類（包括[[Aeromonas_hydrophila|親水性產氣單胞菌]]、[[Hafnia_alvei|哈夫尼亞菌]]和[[Yersinia_enterocolitica|小腸結腸耶氏菌]]）產生的AHL<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Michael, B. |author2=Smith, J.N. |author3=Swift, S. |author4=Heffron, F. |author5=Ahmer, B.M. |title=SdiA of Salmonella enterica is a LuxR homolog that detects mixed microbial communities |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_2001-10_183_19/page/5733 |journal= J. Bacteriol. |volume=183 |issue=19 |pages=5733–42 |date=October 2001 |pmid=11544237 |pmc=95466 |doi=10.1128/JB.183.19.5733-5742.2001}}</ref>。當AHL被偵測到，SdiA調節在沙門氏菌致毒性的質體（pefI–srgD– srgA–srgB-rck-srgC）上的操縱子 ''rck'' 和一個在染色體 ''srgE'' 上的單一基因水平轉移<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Ahmer, B.M. |author2=van Reeuwijk, J. |author3=Timmers, C.D. |author4=Valentine, P.J. |author5=Heffron, F. |title=Salmonella typhimurium encodes an SdiA homolog, a putative quorum sensor of the LuxR family, that regulates genes on the virulence plasmid |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_1998-03_180_5/page/1185 |journal=J. Bacteriol. |volume=180 |issue=5 |pages=1185–93 |date=March 1998 |pmid=9495757 |pmc=107006}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Smith, J.N. |author2=Ahmer, B.M. |title=Detection of other microbial species by Salmonella: expression of the SdiA regulon |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_2003-02_185_4/page/1357 |journal=J. Bacteriol. |volume=185 |issue=4 |pages=1357–66 |date=February 2003 |pmid=12562806 |pmc=142872 |doi=10.1128/JB.185.4.1357-1366.2003}}</ref>。當沙門氏菌通過一些動物的胃腸道時，不會偵測到AHL。這也表明了在正常菌群不會產生AHL。然而，若沙門氏菌在海龜遭受親水性產氣單胞菌寄居，或是大鼠受到小腸結腸炎耶爾森菌感染之時入侵體內，此時即會活化SdiA<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Smith, J.N. |author2=Dyszel, J.L. |author3=Soares, J.A. |title=SdiA, an N-acylhomoserine lactone receptor, becomes active during the transit of Salmonella enterica through the gastrointestinal tract of turtles |journal=PLoS ONE |volume=3 |issue=7 |pages=e2826 |year=2008 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0002826 |pmid=18665275 |pmc=2475663 |editor=Ausubel, Frederick M.|display-authors=etal}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Dyszel, J.L. |author2=Smith, J.N. |author3=Lucas, D.E. |title=Salmonella enterica serovar Typhimurium can detect acyl homoserine lactone production by Yersinia enterocolitica in mice |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_2010-01_192_1/page/n40 |journal=J. Bacteriol. |volume=192 |issue=1 |pages=29–37 |date=January 2010 |pmid=19820103 |doi=10.1128/JB.01139-09 |pmc=2798265|display-authors=etal}}</ref>。因此，沙門氏菌似乎使用SdiA去偵測AHL生產其他病原體，而不是偵測正常的腸道菌群。

==== 綠膿桿菌 ====
[[綠膿桿菌|綠膿桿菌]]是一種伺機性感染菌，會透過群聚感應機制，調控[[生物膜|生物膜]]的形成、{{tsl|en|swarming motility|群體運動|}}、{{tsl|en|exopolysaccharide|外多醣|}}的生產、細菌致毒性以及細胞聚合反應<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Lewis Sauer, K. |author2=Camper, A. |author3=Ehrlich, G. |author4=Costerton, J. |author5=Davies, D. |title=Pseudomonas aeruginosa displays multiple phenotypes during development as a biofilm |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_2002-02_184_4/page/1140 |journal=Journal of Bacteriology |volume=184 |issue=4 |pages=1140–54 |year=2002 |issn=0021-9193 |doi=10.1128/jb.184.4.1140-1154.2002 |pmid=11807075 |pmc=134825}}</ref>。這些細菌在宿主體內生長且不會傷害到宿主，直到細菌濃度達到閾值後，細菌變成較為強勢，並且發展到可以對抗宿主的[[免疫系統|免疫系統]]，並且形成生物膜，導致[[疾病|疾病]]就像細菌擁有生物膜一樣，有一層保護層在宿主的體內。另一種基因調節的形式，允許細菌通過環境信號快速適應的周圍的變化。最近研究發現厭氧菌相可以顯著影響群體感應的主要調節迴路。群體感應和厭氧生物之間的重要聯繫對該生物體的致毒性的產生具有顯著影響<ref name="Cornelis">{{cite book |author=Cornelis, P. (ed.) |title=Pseudomonas: Genomics and Molecular Biology |edition=1st |publisher=Caister Academic Press |year=2008 |url=http://www.horizonpress.com/pseudo |isbn=1-904455-19-0 |access-date=2018-05-22 |archive-date=2016-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160912181431/http://www.horizonpress.com/pseudo |dead-url=no }}</ref>。實驗上，[[大蒜|大蒜]]和[[人參|人參]]可以阻斷綠膿桿菌的群體感應<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Thomas Bjarnsholt |author2=Peter Østrup Jensen |author3=Thomas B. Rasmussen |author4=Lars Christophersen |author5=Henrik Calum |author6=Morten Hentzer |author7=Hans-Petter Hougen |author8=Jørgen Rygaard |author9=Claus Moser |author10=Leo Eberl |author11=Niels Høiby |author12=Michael Givskov  |lastauthoramp=yes |title= Garlic blocks quorum sensing and promotes rapid clearing of pulmonary Pseudomonas aeruginosa infections |journal=Microbiology |volume=151 |issue=4 |pages=3873–80 |year=2005 |pmid=16339933 |doi= 10.1099/mic.0.27955-0}}</ref>。信號分子的治療性酶的降解將阻止這種生物膜的形成並且可能削弱已建立的生物膜。以這種方式中斷信號過程稱為群體感應抑制。

==== 不動桿菌屬 ====
{{tsl|en|Acinetobacter|不動桿菌屬|}}（''Acinetobacter'' sp.）最近已被發現，不動桿菌屬也會表現群體感應。這種細菌是一種新的病原菌，會製造AHL<ref name="biomedcentral">{{cite journal |last=Kok Gan |first=Chan |author2=Atkinson, Steve; Mathee, Kalai; Sam, Choon-Kook; Chhabra, Siri Ram; Camara, Miguel; Koh, Chong-Lek & Williams, Paul |title=Characterization of N-acylhomoserine lactone-degrading bacteria associated with the Zingiber officinale (ginger) rhizosphere: Co-existence of quorum quenching and quorum sensing in Acinetobacter and Burkholderia |journal=BMC Microbiology |year=2011 |volume=11 |pages=51 |doi=10.1186/1471-2180-11-51 |url=http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2180/11/51/abstract |pmid=21385437 |pmc=3062576 |issue=1 |access-date=2018-05-22 |archive-date=2015-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205033643/http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2180/11/51/abstract |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有趣的是不動桿菌屬會同時表現群聚感應和密度感應（quorum quenching）這兩種特性。它會製造AHL也會降解AHL分子<ref name="biomedcentral"/>。

==== 氣單胞菌 ====
{{tsl|en|Aeromonas|氣單胞菌|}}（''Aeromonas sp.''）之前被認為是一種魚類的病原菌<ref>{{cite journal|title=Emerging Aeromonas Species Infections and Their Significance in Public Health| pmc=3373137 | pmid=22701365 | doi=10.1100/2012/625023| volume=2012| year=2012| journal=ScientificWorldJournal| pages=625023 | last1 = Igbinosa | first1 = IH | last2 = Igumbor | first2 = EU | last3 = Aghdasi | first3 = F | last4 = Tom | first4 = M | last5 = Okoh | first5 = AI}}</ref>，但是最近發現是人類的病原菌。單孢菌已經能夠在許多病人的感染部位（膽汁、血液、腹腔液、膿液、糞便和尿液）中分離出來。所有被分離出來的菌株皆生產出兩種主要的AHL（C4-HSL和C6-HSL）。有記錄指出溫和氣單胞菌可以製造C6-HSL以及另外兩個具有N-酰基側鍊長於C6的AHL<ref name="Current Microbiology">{{cite journal |last=Kok Gan |first=Chan |author2=Puthucheary, Savithri D.; Chan, Xin-Yue; Yin, Wai-Fong; Wong, Cheng-Siang; Too, Wah-Seng See & Chua, Kek-Heng |title=Quorum sensing in Aeromonas species isolated from patients in Malaysia |journal=Current Microbiology |year=2010 |volume=62 |pages=167–72 |doi=10.1007/s00284-010-9689-z |url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/m7v48374675257qu/ |pmid=20544198 |issue=1 |author= |access-date=2018-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913091434/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00284-010-9689-z |archive-date=2019-09-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==== 耶爾森氏菌 ====
由[[γ-變形菌綱|γ-變形菌綱]]的{{tsl|en|Yersinia enterocolitica|小腸結腸炎耶爾森菌|}}（''Yersinia enterocolitica''）製造的這兩個蛋白質（YenR和YenI）相似於[[费氏弧菌|费氏弧菌]]的LuxR和Lux<ref name="Atkinson 1451–61">{{cite journal|last=Atkinson|first=S|author2=Chang, CY |author3=Sockett, RE |author4=Cámara, M |author5= Williams, P |title=Quorum sensing in Yersinia enterocolitica controls swimming and swarming motility.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_2006-02_188_4/page/1451|journal=Journal of Bacteriology|date=February 2006|volume=188|issue=4|pages=1451–61|pmid=16452428|doi=10.1128/JB.188.4.1451-1461.2006|pmc=1367215}}</ref>I<ref>{{cite journal|last=Throup|first=JP|author2=Camara, M |author3=Briggs, GS |author4=Winson, MK |author5=Chhabra, SR |author6=Bycroft, BW |author7=Williams, P |author8= Stewart, GS |title=Characterisation of the yenI/yenR locus from Yersinia enterocolitica mediating the synthesis of two N-acylhomoserine lactone signal molecules.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-microbiology_1995-07_17_2/page/345|journal=Molecular Microbiology|date=July 1995|volume=17|issue=2|pages=345–56|pmid=7494483|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2958.1995.mmi_17020345.x}}</ref>。YenR促使{{tsl|en|Bacterial small RNA|小細菌RNA|非編碼的小核糖核酸}}（YenS）的表現。YenS抑制YenI的表現和AHL的製造。YenR、YenI、YenS參與了游泳和成群移動的運動能力的控制<ref name="Atkinson 1451–61" /><ref name="Tsai 556–71">{{cite journal|title=The quorum-hindered transcription factor YenR of Yersinia enterocolitica inhibits pheromone production and promotes motility via a small non-coding RNA.|last=Tsai|first=CS|date=April 2011|journal=Molecular Microbiology|issue=2|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2958.2011.07595.x|volume=80|pages=556–71|pmid=21362062|author2=Winans, SC}}</ref>。

=== 與群體感應相關的分子 ===
2001年，首次發表了涉及群聚感應的蛋白質的三維結構；亦於該年，三種LuxS直向[[同源|同源]]物的[[晶体结构|晶體結構]]藉由[[X射线晶体学|X射線也被確定]]<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Lewis, H.A. |author2=Furlong, E.B. |author3=Laubert, B. |author4=Eroshkina, G.A. |author5=Batiyenko, Y. |author6=Adams, J.M. |author7=Bergseid, M.G. |author8=Marsh, C.D. |author9=Peat, T.S. |author10=Sanderson, W.E. |author11=Sauder, J.M. |author12=Buchanan, S.G. |title=A structural genomics approach to the study of quorum sensing: Crystal structures of three LuxS orthologs |journal=Structure |volume=9 |issue=6 |pages=527–37 |year=2001 |pmid= 11435117 |doi=10.1016/S0969-2126(01)00613-X}}</ref>。2002年，哈維氏弧菌的受器LuxP的晶體結構和它的誘導物AI-2（為少數含[[硼|硼]]的[[生物分子|生物分子]]）與他結合也被確定了<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Chen, X. |author2=Schauder, S. |author3=Potier, N. |author4=Van Dorsselaer, A. |author5=Pelczer, I. |author6=Bassler, B. |author7=Hughson, F. |title=Structural identification of a bacterial quorum-sensing signal containing boron |journal=Nature |volume=415 |issue=6871 |pages=545–9 |year=2002 |pmid=11823863 |url=http://www.nsls.bnl.gov/newsroom/science/2002/pdfs/2002-09-Hughson.pdf |doi=10.1038/415545a |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040622003038/http://www.nsls.bnl.gov/newsroom/science/2002/pdfs/2002-09-Hughson.pdf |archivedate=2004年6月22日 |df= }}</ref>。很多種細菌，包含大腸桿菌及革蘭式陰性細菌的模式生物，都生產AI-2。一個比較基因體學和細菌、古細菌和真核生物的138個基因體樹狀圖演化分析發現酵素LuxS需要AI-2的合成普遍於細菌中。然而，胞質接上{{tsl|en|binding protein|結合蛋白|}}LuxP只存在於弧菌菌株導致的結果不是其他生物體可能使用不同於弧菌菌株的AI-2的訊號傳導系統的成分進行感應AI-2的信號，就是他們並沒有如同群聚感應系統<ref name="pmid15456522">{{cite journal |author1=Sun, J. |author2=Daniel, R. |author3=Wagner-Döbler, I. |author4=Zeng, A.P. |title=Is autoinducer-2 a universal signal for interspecies communication: a comparative genomic and phylogenetic analysis of the synthesis and signal transduction pathways |journal=BMC Evol. Biol. |volume=4 |pages=36 |year=2004 |pmid=15456522 |pmc=524169 |url=http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2148/4/36 |doi=10.1186/1471-2148-4-36 |issue=1 |access-date=2018-05-22 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923203848/http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2148/4/36 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Farnesol|金合歡醇|}}是由真菌[[白色念珠菌|白色念珠菌]]作為一個抑制絲狀的群體感應分子使用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://aem.asm.org/content/67/7/2982.abstract|title=Quorum Sensing in the Dimorphic Fungus Candida albicans Is Mediated by Farnesol|author=Jacob M. Hornby|work=asm.org|accessdate=29 July 2015|archive-date=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203200138/https://aem.asm.org/content/67/7/2982.abstract|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 演化 ===

我們可以使用一個叫做Quorumpeps的資料庫可以藉由搜尋名字的方式分析出群聚感應的胜肽<ref>{{cite journal | year = 2012 | title =  Quorumpeps database: chemical space, microbial origin and functionality of quorum sensing peptides| journal = Nucleic Acids Research | volume = 41| issue = | pages = 1–5 | doi = 10.1093/nar/gks1137 | pmid=23180797 | pmc=3531179 | last1 = Wynendaele | first1 = E | last2 = Bronselaer | first2 = A | last3 = Nielandt | first3 = J | last4 = D'Hondt | first4 = M | last5 = Stalmans | first5 = S | last6 = Bracke | first6 = N | last7 = Verbeke | first7 = F | last8 = Van De Wiele | first8 = C | last9 = De Tré | first9 = G | last10 = De Spiegeleer | first10 = B}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | date = Sep 2015 | title =  Exploring the chemical space of quorum sensing peptides| url = | journal = Biopolymers | volume = 104 | issue = 5| pages = 544–51 | doi = 10.1002/bip.22649 }}</ref>。

某些細菌可以能夠產生可標定和使AHLs不能活化的酶，稱之為{{tsl|en|lactonase|內酰胺酶|}}。研究人員開發了阻斷細菌信號傳導受體的新型分子。mBTL是一種化合物，研究顯示可以抑制群聚感應並且藉由顯著的效果降低細胞死亡的數量<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = O'Loughlin | first1 = CT. | display-authors = etal   | year = 2013 | title = A quorum-sensing inhibitor blocks Pseudomonas aeruginosa virulence and biofilm formation | url = | journal = PNAS | volume = 110 | issue = 44| pages = 17981–6 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.1316981110 }}</ref>。此外，研究人員也研究利用天然化合物（如咖啡因）作為有可能抑制群聚感應角色<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Norizan | first1 = S. | last2 = Chan | first2 = K. | year = 2013 | title = Caffeine as a potential quorum-sensing inhibitor | url = | journal = Sensors | volume = 13 | issue = 4| pages = 5117–5129 | doi = 10.3390/s130405117 }}</ref>。在這領域的研究是有希望的，並且可以導致天然化合物作為有效治療劑的發展。這項研究有機會將天然化合物發展為具有療效的治療藥劑。

